            <note xml:id="foot.f2">CD refers to <ref target="../nameregs/nameregs_3047.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">Vernon Lushington</ref>. See <ref target="./DCP-LETT-6654.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">letter from T. H. Huxley, 11 March 1869</ref> and n. 1.</note>
